%N A039106 Numbers whose base-9 representation has the same number of 5's and 6's.
%H A039106 Chris R. Rehmann, <a href="/A039106/b039106.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%t A039106 Select[Range[0, 21531], DigitCount[#, 9, 5]==DigitCount[#, 9, 6]&] (* _Chris R. Rehmann_, Mar 25 2026 *)
%o A039106 (MATLAB) x = 0:21531; d = dec2base(x,9)-'0'; a = x(sum(d==5,2)==sum(d==6,2)); disp(regexprep(num2str(a), ' +', ', ')) % _Chris R. Rehmann_, Mar 25 2026
